race.description: M.j. Dale Racing Country Boosted Mdn Plate
race.comment: SACRED INFERNO (8) can bring up a race-to-race double for the in-form Seib stable. He's been narrowly beaten all three race starts and last time there was only a nose in it over this trip at Moruya. STORMBRINGER (3) resumes and has switched to Matt Dale from Waterhouse-Bott on a 198-day return. He placed this trip on debut and raced over further following. Has good ability and a key gear switch. The late betting will be key. SLATER'S BOY (2) was narrowly beaten here first-up off a long break. He has plenty of scope for improvement and maps well. Keep him very safe. Stablemate ELASAND (9) reaches peak fitness but needs to spike his numbers to be winning.
